House of Fabrics Inc &lt;HF>said it expects further modest gains in revenues for fiscalyear ending January 31, 1988.    In fiscal 1987, the company's revenues were 316.4 mln dlrscompared to 286.7 mln dlrs the previous fiscal year endingJanuary 31.    House of Fabrics President and Chief executive, GaryLarkins, said the company will be aggressively promoting saleswhile applying tighter inventory controls. Reuter&#3;